            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row d-flex flex-row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 font7 text-end">
              <p>1.Ticketing and Boarding: Passengers need valid tickets to board the plane.</p>
              <p>2.Baggage: Follow rules on baggage size, weight, and prohibited items.</p>
              <p>3.Safety Briefings: Listen to safety instructions before takeoff.</p>
              <p>4.Seat Belts: Fasten seat belts during takeoff, landing, and when instructed.</p>
              <p>5.Behavior: Respect crew instructions and fellow passengers.</p>
              <p>6.Smoking and Alcohol: No smoking; alcohol consumption must be responsible.</p>
              <p>7.Electronic Devices: Follow rules on device usage during flight.</p>
              <p>8.Health: Inform the airline of any medical needs.</p>
              <p>9.Rights: Know your rights regarding delays, cancellations, and baggage issues.</p>
              <p>10.Customs and Immigration: Comply with customs and immigration regulations when traveling internationally.</p>
              <p>These regulations aim to ensure that passengers have a safe, comfortable, and hassle-free experience when flying and outline their rights and responsibilities during air travel.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
              <img src="./Images/Rules.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            </div>  
          </div>
